Syntype series (
Breedy et al. 2009
): MCZ 723 [dry]; MCZ 7080 [dry]; YPM 1551a-d and 1629a, b [dry]; YPM 5146 [dry].

Red gorgonian (
Gotshall 1998
).

Generally found on offshore reefs and islands; prefers clean, plankton-rich waters and generally found at depths to ~30 m (
Gotshall 1998
).
